7 Aug 2019 Minister in the Presidency, Jackson Mthembu will brief media on outcomes of the Cabinet meeting held on Wednesday, the 7th of August 2019. Members of the media are invited as follows: Date:  Thursday, 8 August 2019Time: 12h30Venue: GCIS Ronnie Mamoepa Media Room, 1035 Tshedimosetso House, Frances Baard Street, Hatfield NB: There will be a video link to Imbizo Media Centre, 120 Plein Street, Parliament, Cape Town Follow the conversation on @GovernmentZA @GCISMedia #PostCabinet Enquiries:Phumla Williams, GCIS Acting Director-GeneralCell: 083 501 0139 Issued by: Goverment Communication and Information System